LG Electronics has said its goal is to continuously leverage on latest innovations and technology to help consumers live a better, more convenient, and fulfilling life that they deserve. The company stated this yesterday as it highlighted the features of its LG XBoom GO all-in-one solutions and ultra-convenient bluetooth speakers. LG Electronics said, ‘‘Dubbed the LG XBoom Go PL, the portable speaker is part of the XBoom lineup of bluetooth speakers first introduced in the market in 2020, imed at delivering powerful sounds and ultimate ease- of-use, the LG XBoom Go PL comes in two models – PL7 and PL5. The LG XBoom Go PL Series (5 & 7) has but one goal in mind: to get the party started.’’ According to the product manager, Home Entertainment, Audio Visual Division, LG Electronics West African Operations, Mr. Daesun Hwang, “With these new speakers, users get greater versatility thanks to its advanced portability and connectivity options that support excellent audio quality any time or place, keeping the music playing and the good times rolling”, he said. ‘‘Given the LG XBoom Go PL7 is aimed at party people, it comes as no surprise that the device offers IPX5 water resistance.